OL,3,CUniversities call for students to pay
OL,4,Chigher fees to solve funding issues
OL,6,FA group representing dozens of UK
OL,7,Funiversities has called for higher
OL,8,Fstudent fees and more government
OL,9,Ffunding to tackle a financial black
OL,10,Fhole.
OL,12,FUniversities UK (UUK) said government
OL,13,Fgrants and fees have not kept pace
OL,14,Fwith rising costs, causing budget
OL,15,Fdeficits.
OL,17,FTuition fees for home students in
OL,18,FEngland have been capped at #9,250
OL,19,Fsince 2017.
