OL,3,CUniversities call for students to pay
OL,4,Chigher fees to solve funding issues
OL,6,F"We are alert to the fact, of course,
OL,7,Fthat when you say fees should go up,
OL,8,Fpeople are alarmed at the consequences
OL,9,Ffor students, which is why we also
OL,10,Fthink that it's very important that
OL,11,Fthe support that students get in terms
OL,12,Fof maintenance loans and grants also
OL,13,Fbe looked at."
OL,15,FUUK's proposals suggest that if
OL,16,Finvestment in teaching students had
OL,17,Fkept up with inflation, funding per
OL,18,Fstudent would be in the region of
OL,19,F#12,000-#13,000.
